description: The new albums Quantum Baby and Bird's Eye are exercises in self-liberation, leveraging the sounds and potential of a loaded category while rejecting its limits.
title: Tinashe and Ravyn Lenae lean into the paradox of 'alt-R&B'

description: Survivors and organizers of the Nova Music Festival in Israel where hundreds were killed or taken hostage created an exhibit called “October 7, 6:29am — The Moment the Music Stood Still.”
title: Nova massacre memorial comes to Southern California

description: The Food and Drug Administration is expected to give the green light to new COVID-19 vaccines this week to protect against recent variants of the coronavirus.
title: Updated COVID vaccines are coming soon

description: Both of Canada’s major freight railroads have come to a full stop because of a contract dispute with their workers, an impasse that may bring economic disruption in Canada and the U.S.
title: Labor dispute stops Canadian rail freight and could cause economic disruption in U.S.

description: Jon Polin and Rachel Goldberg, parents of Hersh Goldberg-Polin held hostage by Hamas in Gaza since Oct. 7, took to the podium at the DNC calling for a cease-fire deal so that the 109 remaining Hamas hostages can return home.
title: Parents of Hersh Goldberg-Polin call for Oct. 7 hostages to return home in remarks at the DNC

description: Obama wore a navy sleeveless jacket with crisscross, reconstructed lapels in front that she paired with matching trousers. The more than $2,500 fit came from luxury fashion brand Monse's resort 2025 collection and it's left the internet in shambles.
title: Former First Lady Michelle Obama's suit sets the internet on fire
